trans-unit.source: See the Package Documentation for information on installation and usage.
trans-unit.target: 有关安装和使用的信息,请参见软件包文档。

trans-unit.source: pyKML is a Python package for parsing and authoring KML documents. It is based on the lxml.objectify API (http://codespeak.net/lxml/objectify.html) which provides Pythonic access to XML documents.
trans-unit.target: pyKML is a Python package for parsing and authoring KML documents. It is based on the lxml.objectify API (http://codespeak.net/lxml/objectify.html) which provides Pythonic access to XML documents.
